channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Crockett Mocked Into Next Week for Huge Mistake She Made While Trying to Raise Money Off Fight With MTG
Maryland governor signs Biden-inspired bill establishing 'Center for Firearm Violence Prevention'
item.description: Democratic Maryland governor Wes Moore signed a law creating the Center for Firearm Violence Prevention and Intervention, modeled after President Biden's gun violence office.

item.title: Bernie Moreno to Newsmax: Sen. Brown's Policies Hurt Middle Class
item.description: Bernie Moreno, the Republican Senate candidate in Ohio, told Newsmax on Saturday that "a great middle-class life has been stripped away from us" thanks to the policies of his opponent, Democrat Sen. Sherrod Brown.

item.title: BREAKING: Gun Fired During Kansas City HS Graduation Ceremony, 1 Person 'Potentially Deceased'
Trump demands Biden 'drug test,' rips 'radical' RFK Jr. in bid to 'rebellious bunch' at NRA
item.description: Former President Trump fired up supporters at the National Rifle Association's Annual Meeting, demanding that President Biden get a drug test before the pair debates.

item.title: Trump: 'Our Constitution Is Being Run Through the Shredder'
item.description: Presumptive Republican presidential nominee Donald Trump warned the Second Amendment is under "siege" and the Constitution is being put through the shredder.

item.title: Houthis Attack Oil Tanker in Red Sea With Missile After Biden Just Begged Iran to Make Them Stop
DC Mayor Bowser jets off for Las Vegas weekend 'mission' after ritzy Masters trip on taxpayers' dime
item.description: Washington D.C. Mayor Muriel Bowser will travel to Las Vegas this weekend less than a month after she faced scrutiny for attending the Masters on the taxpayers dime.

item.title: Despite Polls, Biden Aides Insist Gaza Campus Protests Will Not Hurt Reelection Bid
item.description: Several top White House aides say they are confident protests across U.S. college campuses against Israel's offensive in Gaza will not translate into significantly fewer votes for Joe Biden in November's election, despite polls showing many Democrats are deeply unhappy...

item.title: Disney's Latest Act of Self-Immolation Is As Culturally Stupid As It Is Financially Dumb
In Israel visit, Stefanik to tout Trump's record on Jewish state, reject Biden policies: 'No excuse'
item.description: House GOP Conference Chair Elise Stefanik, R-N.Y., will deliver passionate remarks in support of Israel at the Knesset Sunday morning with pointed criticism of President Biden.

item.title: 6 Penn Students Among 19 Arrested for Trying to Occupy Building
item.description: Six University of Pennsylvania students were among 19 pro-Palestinian protesters arrested during an attempt to occupy a school building, university police said Saturday.

item.title: South Dakota Gov Kristi Noem Brings Quiet Fire to the California GOP Convention
Missouri Sen. Josh Hawley defends 'friend' Harrison Butker after 'out of touch' left's 'absurd meltdown'
item.description: Senator Josh Hawley defended his "friend" Harrison Butker this week on social media after both media and the NFL condemned the kicker's commencement address.

item.title: RNC, Trump Campaign Launch 'Gun Owners for Trump'
item.description: Before delivering his remarks at NRA Leadership Forum in Dallas on Saturday night, the Republican National Committee and the Trump campaign announced the launch of the Gun Owners for Trump coalition.
